{"tid":1674504,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"第一屆連登時代革命備忘錄接龍大比拚！","createTime":"2019-10-25T08:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T10:43:23.000Z","uid":36169,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1b5fd32c9f2b72a0cbcd3d8618cdd7504e4d8993","tid":1674504,"uid":36169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:59:09.000Z","msg":"由於香港係十分善忘嘅生物！<br />\n由6.9至今大家仲記唔記得出現過幾多駭人嘅場面！（因為我見大家已經努力選區議會）<br />\n<br />\n光復香港不能一朝一夕，眼見小學生都會上街參與，我相信革命嘅火種同決心係可以薪火相傳！<br />\n<br />\n我想做到由革命開始至今的抗拒畫面同地方文宣相片又好，都可以好似希哥的閃卡咁，就算dl唔翻，但都可以睇到大家入曬腦，畫都畫得翻出嚟，即使以後點比人打壓，點比人封網，都封唔到大家嘅腦同決心！<br />\n<br />\n玩法如下：<br />\n上家出題：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hwt5zy5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhwt5zy5.jpg&h=238a3f08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下家接龍：<br />\n元朗 八鄉 指揮官 李漢民<br />\n係721白衫打人事後一個半小時先出現，喺面對記者嘅鏡頭同詢問時，表示：你咁樣係唔會令到我驚㗎！<br />\n<br />\n_________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n請接：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD9Acnd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD9Acnd.jpg&h=44622f1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b180ab7d2ff507c150fa276246e69092af83d8f","tid":1674504,"uid":36169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:13:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ab857c15be0fe207ba71115edb2eeb4be534889","tid":1674504,"uid":36169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"347f58a62929c83a0c419b300e17ed63f98965f3","tid":1674504,"uid":36169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:58:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c21e07d1e290d11d7d8bb73ce661d0b0efc3f579","tid":1674504,"uid":36169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:58:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d7ccb86c39ebc5c5dd6889e710ded0d6ef8f6a9","tid":1674504,"uid":36169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:58:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"062de49c6319564195